  22 Jul 2015; James Le Cuirot <chewi@gentoo.org> jre-1.7.0.ebuild:
  Keyword ~ppc.

  21 Jul 2015; James Le Cuirot <chewi@gentoo.org> jre-1.6.0-r1.ebuild:
  Drop 1.6 on arm as newer versions with HotSpot are preferable.

  11 Jul 2015; James Le Cuirot <chewi@gentoo.org> jre-1.6.0-r1.ebuild,
  jre-1.7.0.ebuild, jre-1.8.0.ebuild:
  Drop java on ia64.

